  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK772">
<l>kāṉa muyaleyta vampiṉiṉ yāṉai</l>
<l>piḻaittavē lēnta liṉitu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>It is more pleasant to hold the dart that has missed an elephant than that which has hit hare in the forest.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
